---
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label">01 / about</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">About me</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="copy">
        <p>
          I'm a full-stack engineer based in North Dandenong, Australia. I picked up
          programming through <a href="https://www.codecademy.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Codecademy's Full-Stack Engineer</a>
          track and have since been building projects that push me beyond tutorial-land —
          real databases, real auth flows, real deployment headaches.
        </p>
        <p>
          My most recent project is a
          <a href="https://blogging-platform-pearl-six.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">blogging platform</a>
          with a rich-text editor built on Lexical, Google OAuth, S3 image uploads, and a
          fully typed React + Express stack. It taught me more about authentication,
          state management, and deployment than any course ever did.
        </p>
        <p>Technologies I work with:</p>
        <ul class="stack-list">
          <li>TypeScript</li>
          <li>React / Redux</li>
          <li>Node.js / Express</li>
          <li>PostgreSQL</li>
          <li>AWS (S3, EC2)</li>
          <li>Docker</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="portrait">
        <div class="portrait-frame">
          <p class="portrait-label">At a glance</p>
          <dl class="portrait-list">
            <div class="row"><dt>Name</dt><dd>Yasin Wafazada</dd></div>
            <div class="row"><dt>Role</dt><dd>Full-stack engineer</dd></div>
            <div class="row"><dt>Based in</dt><dd>Melbourne, Australia</dd></div>
            <div class="row"><dt>Certified</dt><dd>Codecademy, 2024</dd></div>
            <div class="row"><dt>Status</dt><dd><span class="available">Available for hire</span></dd></div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .copy p { margin-bottom: 1.1rem; color: var(--fg-muted); }
  .copy p:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .stack-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0.4rem 1.5rem;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .stack-list li {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--fg);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }
  .stack-list li::before {
    content: "▸";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .portrait-frame {
    position: relative;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-hi);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    background: var(--bg-alt);
  }
  .portrait-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }
  .portrait-list {
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.9rem;
  }
  .portrait-list .row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 90px 1fr;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .portrait-list dt {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .portrait-list dd {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--fg);
  }
  .portrait-frame::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: -6px -6px auto auto;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--accent);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 0 6px 0 0;
  }
  .portrait-frame::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: auto auto -6px -6px;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 0 0 0 6px;
  }
  .available { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
